videos.headline: Ovechkin speechless after Holtby's save
videos.description: Alex Ovechkin reacts to Braden Holtby's incredible save that preserved the Capitals' Game 2 victory over the Golden Knights.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Ovechkin speechless after Holtby's save) 2018/05/30

videos.headline: Fleury doesn't appreciate Holtby's save
videos.description: Marc-Andre Fleury says Braden Holtby's save was good, but he wanted it to go in so the Golden Knights could avoid trouble with a loss in Game 2.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Fleury doesn't appreciate Holtby's save) 2018/05/30

videos.headline: Capitals look to overcome Kuznetsov's injury
videos.description: Greg Wyshynski and Emily Kaplan explain the Capitals' mood after Braden Holtby's save in Game 2 and what Evgeny Kuznetsov's injury means.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Capitals look to overcome Kuznetsov's injury) 2018/05/30
